Method Detail

compareTo

public int compareTo(TimeInstant ti)
Compares chronologically current TimeInstant object and ti parameter. Result is the difference between the conversion obained with toMinutes for current and parameter object, giving: - negative when current TimeInstant is previous to ti - zero if they are equal - positive when current TimeInstant is posterior to ti
